Package: NOAATides
Type: Package
Title: Collect Ocean Tides Data From NOAA
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "Warlick", email = "warlick.sean@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Sean Warlick <warlick.sean@gmail.com>
Description: The NOAATides package provides a small set of tools for collecting
    tides data from NOAA.  The functions provided in the package are wrappers around
    NOAA's existing APIs.
